<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1906-06-30T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1906-06-30T00:00:00-05:00" n="374" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d374">
                        <head><hi rend="italic">Minister <persName type="from">Barrett</persName> to
                                the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi></head>
                        <opener><seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg></opener>
                        <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>,<lb/><hi rend="italic">Bogotá</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1906-06-30"><hi rend="italic">June 30,
                                1906</hi></date>.</dateline></opener>
                        <p>(Mr. Barrett transmits a request of the President of Colombia that public
                            announcement be made in the United States of the preliminary
                            negotiations initiated in Colombia, and of the contemplated appointment
                            of Sehor Enrique Cortes as minister of Colombia on Secretary Root’s
                            return from his visit to South American Republics.)</p>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>